BTG Close to Merger Deal With Colombia Correval, Republica Says

-- B y   A n d r e a   J a r a m i l l o
-- 
2011-09-16T14:29:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/btg-close-to-merger-deal-with-colombia-correval-republica-says.html
Banco BTG Pactual SA, the Brazilian
investment bank founded by billionaire  Andre Esteves , is close
to a merger deal with Colombian brokerage Correval SA, La
Republica newspaper reported, without saying where it got the
information.  A Correval spokesman in Bogota wasn’t immediately available
for comment when contacted by Bloomberg News. A BTG official in
 Sao Paulo  didn’t comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Jaramillo in Bogota at 
 ajaramillo1@bloomberg.net  